            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-mist-200 rounded-3xl p-7">
          <div class="flex gap-0.5 text-[#F5B81F] text-base mb-3">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="text-ink text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            "I stopped freezing when investors push back. The behavioral analysis showed me exactly why... and what to do instead. Worth every penny."
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <img src="/images/avatar-2-peace.webp" alt="" class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full" />
            <div>
              <div class="font-bold text-sm">James R.</div>
